name: The Fly
description: “Have you ever heard of insect politics? Neither have I. Insects don't have politics. They're very brutal. No compassion, no compromise. We can't trust the insect. I'd like to become the first insect politician. I'm saying I… I'm an insect who dreamt he was a man and loved it. But now the dream is over and the insect is awake.” - The Fly
